{"tid":1430304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔:粉嶺今晚要戒嚴!邊個出街就係鬼!","createTime":"2019-08-07T17:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T17:50:26.000Z","uid":2871,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"41ba93af864f6d6a598cc578b011a6eb32deb8e6","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:00:06.000Z","msg":"事源:<br />\n有張咁既圖係昨日流傳上Facebook 各北區group<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FkW7FKX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkW7FKX.jpg&h=05ed8230&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n到今日就開始多人討論到底咩事，邊個搞集會。仲要係粉火橋。<br />\n的確依個位置比較尷尬，地方細，放工人流又多。行多兩步仲係PTU總部。<br />\n咁就開始有唔同既風開始吹 <br />\n例如：一定有鬼，到時會就會有老黑搞事/有狗扮人挑釁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就重演深水埗事件(拉人&gt;聲援&gt;出防暴&gt;送頭)<br />\n唔少商店都提早落閘 狗屋又落閘 宿舍又水馬<br />\n<br />\n由於個風愈吹愈大，連登就開始有相關既澄清post出現。<br />\n今晚粉嶺無示威無集會！無吹雞！無需協助入粉嶺！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1428731/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1428731/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我宣佈今晚除咗粉嶺居民，邊個入粉嶺邊個就係鬼！走啦仆街，咪撚入粉嶺啊！屌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1429093/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1429093/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dwn3d4Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDwn3d4Y.png&h=26e2f1c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第2個POST既樓豬話要同出席既人割 仲話街坊係鬼 要打!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你冇撚野呀?</span></span></strong><br />\n屌你為件事好絕對唔係用依類方式，進行自我閹割。<br />\n你話搵唔到搞手 冇人負責 位置差 唔適合 我都理解<br />\n但係連咩無不反對通知書 係非法集會 拉得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上水狗署 PTU總部好近呀 散啦 咪搞啦 搞少日係咪會死?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我先知原來狗同老黑植入既白色恐怖原來咁成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n集會自由都自我放棄啦 應驗晒 &ldquo;驚就唔好出街&rdquo; 斬腳趾避沙蟲<br />\n連個50歲既呀叔都識走出黎話 本身都驚今晚有事<br />\n但係諗多兩諗就深知唔可以驚 仲拎埋支柺杖落樓!<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>反觀連登仔：不了！散了！</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來咩727元朗反黑遊行係佢地心目中係一個大笑話!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我講咁撚柒多 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實我只希望大家可以戰勝恐懼，難道真係連搞一個和理非聚會都要怕?</span></span><br />\n其實黑狗要搞鳩你，你唔集會一樣可以搞。<br />\n的確搞手係搞得唔太好，但係都充分反映出大家既過度反應。<br />\n希望大家之後可以冷靜對應。"},{"pid":"144929cfc2215bdedfb6e2690ef956d1dcdff245","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:02:33.000Z","msg":"唔係堆狗做場大龍鳳，叫人早收就要怕!<br />\n要對抗佢地玩白色恐怖就正正係要行出黎!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同買觀星筆一樣!"},{"pid":"3492601114a5ef2cb216e2a26a026a422b154647","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511bb4955e1ea79d923acc3dd7df2dccfaf85737","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:08:15.000Z","msg":"10連開始!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第1連!"},{"pid":"14da59284b0fbd3cf90a0c3ee6f3f8f341686ecf","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:08:33.000Z","msg":"第2連!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e63c3a190f32491ad522e46603012e7941f5968","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:08:46.000Z","msg":"第3連!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d24f6e0a3072900c24b3c54a741b98441515cb","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"第4連!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434fb4d4576473bc35820c911e896c93b52c5c80","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:09:18.000Z","msg":"第5連!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1332dc59d8849e71f1e6e60eaeda53a88ebc77d0","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:09:31.000Z","msg":"第6連!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377a7ead7a21d615ec21c61374322b86ee9670ac","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:09:42.000Z","msg":"第7連!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aaceee6f34918359ff9d7e46ba16bde2f213349","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:10:00.000Z","msg":"第8連!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8741cad0bb45eb47f2bec4a40a1d6d288b6131e","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"第9連!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e2a21f24448e4d6d7c6b241807abe53d3b2429","tid":1430304,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:10:21.000Z","msg":"連一連你"},{"pid":"8500f4112543f37a47093adf78bcd136b9d980b1","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"第10連!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18ea8dfa31112a3f3ce717a8c64b677100277f0","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37e2a21f24448e4d6d7c6b241807abe53d3b2429","tid":1430304,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:10:21.000Z","msg":"連一連你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:11:02.000Z","msg":"比你斷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9abfa41a27805433c8bf386243b83008b5e97ac3","tid":1430304,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d18ea8dfa31112a3f3ce717a8c64b677100277f0","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37e2a21f24448e4d6d7c6b241807abe53d3b2429","tid":1430304,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:10:21.000Z","msg":"連一連你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:11:02.000Z","msg":"比你斷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9493efd58fbd83fbb6f42d047056ac014f25ef64","tid":1430304,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:13:45.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"e6cbf274b014aa3f8525bcb25c75a8429ed62371","tid":1430304,"uid":168703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"今晚夜左訓，終於比我見到夜間工作嘅引戰撚。"},{"pid":"100f99ae627c77791752011df534f011678058d7","tid":1430304,"uid":113250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:20:14.000Z","msg":"屌，其實只係叫附近的居民集下氣吹下水姐，因為之前有單傷人案，同埋粉火連儂日日俾人清，所以想叫多啲人注意同埋幫手姐，好似係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4203ab9095898d95a7b3fb3ec041f0aad9280d","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6cbf274b014aa3f8525bcb25c75a8429ed62371","tid":1430304,"uid":168703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"今晚夜左訓，終於比我見到夜間工作嘅引戰撚。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"第2個POST我直頭睇到呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4caabf41b6d22c0b30045cefe5d3b32508861327","tid":1430304,"uid":26030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"100f99ae627c77791752011df534f011678058d7","tid":1430304,"uid":113250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:20:14.000Z","msg":"屌，其實只係叫附近的居民集下氣吹下水姐，因為之前有單傷人案，同埋粉火連儂日日俾人清，所以想叫多啲人注意同埋幫手姐，好似係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"根本熟個頭就知個邊個地理位置有咩問題<br />\n根本一出事好難走<br />\n而樓主咁夜開啲個post 居心叵測"},{"pid":"14220ad4fad18d5414f2962949741147a2372dd7","tid":1430304,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:30:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不推文回覆</span><br />\n<br />\n夜啦，用返個腦上連登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1e0e1fad6aacaefa9bf00a118098920c621a4c","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4caabf41b6d22c0b30045cefe5d3b32508861327","tid":1430304,"uid":26030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"100f99ae627c77791752011df534f011678058d7","tid":1430304,"uid":113250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:20:14.000Z","msg":"屌，其實只係叫附近的居民集下氣吹下水姐，因為之前有單傷人案，同埋粉火連儂日日俾人清，所以想叫多啲人注意同埋幫手姐，好似係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"根本熟個頭就知個邊個地理位置有咩問題<br />\n根本一出事好難走<br />\n而樓主咁夜開啲個post 居心叵測"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:37:17.000Z","msg":"我會唔知?<br />\n講真搞手揀個咁既位就一定係有問題 根本人多少少都塞死晒 出事分分鐘跳橋係冇錯。<br />\n但係絕對唔係用上面果2個POST入面部份人製造恐慌既論調。<br />\n唔好Spin我個論點 而且你咁夜都覆我啦 難道你又居心叵測?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc068dd3392fef5ee7d7b71c549fdb2d6ec3e9f","tid":1430304,"uid":26030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:42:50.000Z","msg":"試下個不推文回覆先<br />\n當前幾日有人拎把鎚出黎係同一個位扑人<br />\n而到夜晚先突然有一班人叫人去集會<br />\n總合返種種跡象有懷疑我相信係好合理<br />\n我知道本身放映會搞手係有心人士<br />\n但係咪今日會俾人騎劫既機會係零呢?<br />\n當然你可以馬後炮話根本無事發生<br />\n但個個位人多少少已經會塞死晒<br />\n提早有擔心想問呢個係咩問題?"},{"pid":"5de80a140fd461c5e7510bc117a07f9b7e9f5114","tid":1430304,"uid":2871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:43:39.000Z","msg":"講真開得依個POST都預左有人負評 想負就負 冇問題 大家討論。<br />\n因為搞手方面 地理方面的確係有問題。<br />\n而我出依個POST既重點係叫大家唔好過份反應，要冷靜應對。<br />\n以上面2個POST入面部份既論調黎計 咁其實好多遊行/行動都唔撚洗搞。<br />\n何況依個只係一個和非理街坊分享會..."}]}